title: Check out the latest and greatest version of Denver Intl Airport (KDEN) from a new developer!
description:
Denver International Airport has been featured numerous times in marketplace review videos. Yet here it is once more, the same airport but from a different developer. This developer has infused a wealth of detail into the airport, surpassing the standard scenery included in MSFS. Therefore, if you frequently fly in this region, it would be worthwhile to explore this add-on.

For a full overview of items added to the marketplace this week have a look at the video below:
